{
  "stem": "24885.3",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And there was a grave, I understand, one of them with quite a few people or maybe a thousand that they just shot-- people who couldn't walk to the train station, people who couldn't-- when they liquidate them or whatever happened.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But yeah, I know what happened because all my 40-- almost 40-- the 40 of them were from the same area, and all of them died in one day.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yeah.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "As a matter of fact, the officer who came to the supply house to get food for them brought me regards from so and so, you know?",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I would ask him-- once you get closer to them, they'd talk sometime.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Not that he was a friend of mine, but I told him tell so and so that I asked for him.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he would come back the next week and say, so he's doing good.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I'm sure he did because they were very friendly to me because I was in the position where I distributed them food and their wine, their liquor, their everything.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So I was accepted.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The 40?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No, I don't know.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I know they were killed.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "All right.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Then one day, there was, in '44-- also in the summertime-- one of our-- there was-- we were a small group in there, maybe 15 or 20 people.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "One Jewish man escaped.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And it didn't take long for them to come down from the concentration camp, from the ammunition factory, gather us all up.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "No, no this.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I was called up from work at 12 o'clock, asked to come outside, and marched into the-- into the concentration camp without connection with the ammunition factory.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We stayed there about approximately two months or less.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, Konzentrationslager.",
      "word_count": 2
    }
  ],
